{"tid":1724052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不用代購了？中國蒙牛成功收購澳洲奶粉廠商Bellamy's","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:44:17.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c18f8234cd06e42540737985a61500c567e99341","tid":1724052,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"不用代購了？中國成功收購澳洲奶粉廠商<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/11/15/realtime/7071148.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F11%2F15%2Frealtime%2F7071148.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=cad04859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲外國投資審查委員會（FIRB）15日批准中國大陸蒙牛乳業以澳幣約14億3000萬元（台幣302億元），收購有機嬰兒配方奶粉廠商Bellamy's。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲財長費登伯格（Josh Frydenberg）表示該收購案未違反澳洲國家利益，不過，收購附加條件，包括Bellamy's總部必須留在澳洲至少10年，同時董事會成員多數必須是居住在澳洲的澳洲公民。<br />\n<br />\nFIRB同時也要求蒙牛乳業投資至少澳幣1200萬元在維多利亞省的奶粉加工工廠。<br />\n<br />\nBellamy's在澳洲奶粉市場銷售額排名第四，15日午盤價位澳幣13.20元，比蒙牛乳業9月宣布要以每股13.25元收購價格略低。<br />\n<br />\n費登伯格在聲明中表示，「這項合作能讓Bellamy's繼續提供澳洲人工作機會，並且強化其擴張國內市場和國外出口的能力，尤其是亞洲市場。這項決定也將提供Bellamy's乳製品廠商，像是澳洲酪農工作機會」。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，「澳洲政府歡迎與國家利益相符的國外投資。若沒有國外資金和投資，澳洲的出口、工作機會和生活條件會較低」。<br />\n<br />\nBellamy's董事會一致建議股東在下個月的會議同意收購案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4167069?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F4167069%3Ffrom%3Dudn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=777e1ddf\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4167069?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news</a>"},{"pid":"edb231cd8fc798e3b89345ffe140e2d0e7b080c5","tid":1724052,"uid":73619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"Wa 以後唔洗飲"},{"pid":"daaa0e5cce8a23422fdcbbeb9ef3960f7a48ba80","tid":1724052,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"澳共"},{"pid":"dba016cfd15519a53524de0b793d77764c84b045","tid":1724052,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/11/15/realtime/7071148.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F11%2F15%2Frealtime%2F7071148.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=cad04859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港有無出售？"},{"pid":"d02f6db31886a6ff36997d01fa3b8156c47232cd","tid":1724052,"uid":236368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"正吖，個個變大頭B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87def417feb7f84a605410024c02efea66d1a5f","tid":1724052,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:05:27.000Z","msg":"蒙牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18fba6ae5e8605b288eb655907c68826ab52f79","tid":1724052,"uid":212878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d02f6db31886a6ff36997d01fa3b8156c47232cd","tid":1724052,"uid":236368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"正吖，個個變大頭B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1b29dcad93c5522ea37495cf9f8954abe717a8","tid":1724052,"uid":35790,"l